- Hello, this is a flight reservation system which has many key features and I will add some more in the future
- Key features:
    - Add airline - Admin Feature
    - Add Flight - Admin Feature
    - Remove Flight - Admin Feature
    - Book a ticket
    - Cancel a ticket
    - Look up available flights
    - Register to the system and have your flights saved
    - Auto generation of a seat with each ticket
    - Auto generation of a flight number also with the airlines acronym attached

- Planned Features:
    - Each flight has a specific amount of seats
    - Seat generation is also dependent on the aircraft type and not just a generic number i've put
    - Faster searching algorithims for looking through data
    - Local database to store information such as flights, airlines, customers, admin accounts, tickets booked.


- Hopefully this small little application is of use to someone in the future and can aid them in their path to creating their own
  system like this one or even a better one which may include a GUI or some sort of websites to go alongside it. However, I believe
  that focusing on the internals is the most important thing before you start to get all arts and crafty. Other than that, I have tested
  everything and it should all be working fine however if there any issues then I challenge you to fix them and improve on them. Lastly, with
  the planned features I aim to add. If I do not do it then that can also be a challenge for you also :)


